'''藍緻密矮星系'''（'''BCD星系'''）是[[天文學|天文學]]上對擁有年輕、炙熱、大質量恆星組成大星團的小[[星系|星系]]所給的名稱，而這些恆星使星系的顏色偏藍<ref name="darling">[http://www.daviddarling.info/encyclopedia/B/blue_compact_dwarf_galaxy.html blue compact dwarf galaxy (BCD)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.daviddarling.info/encyclopedia/B/blue_compact_dwarf_galaxy.html |date=20190816002830 }}, David Darling, entry in ''The Internet Encyclopedia of Science''. Accessed on line [[October_14|October 14]], 2007.</ref>。鄰近的例子有[[NGC_1705|NGC 1705]]、[[NGC_2915|NGC 2915]]和[[NGC_3353|NGC 3353]]<ref name="darling" /><ref>[http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1994AJ....107.2021M Optical observations of NGC 2915: A nearby blue compact dwarf galaxy] {{Wayback|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1994AJ....107.2021M |date=20170721142308 }}, G. R. Meurer, G. Mackie and C. Carignan, ''The Astronomical Journal'' '''107''', #6 (June 1994), pp. 2021–2035.</ref>。

